<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٠٣٠ -<span style="color:#006d98"> قَالَ:</span> وَكَانَ عُرْوَةُ،<span style="color:#006d98"> يَقُولُ:</span> ⦗١٠٥٢⦘ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«أَزْهَدُ النَّاسِ فِي عَالِمٍ أَهْلُهُ»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>